		<tu tuid="common-voice:web/locales/en/cross-locale.ftl:get-involved-text" srclang="en-US">
			<tuv xml:lang="en-US">
				<seg>Thank you for your interest in contributing to { $lang }. We work hard to get every language ready for launch and keep
the teams updated via email. If you want to contribute, please provide your email below.</seg>
			</tuv>
			<tuv xml:lang="bm">
				<seg>I ni ce I ka timinanjiya la { $langBamanankan } sankɔrɔtanni la. Anw bɛ cɛsirila walasa ka kanw bɛɛ lakodɔn ani ka ba‌arakɛɲɔgɔnw kunnafoni imɛyi fɛ. N'Aw b'a fɛ ka aw ka bólomafara lase, A y'aw  ka imayi sɛbɛn duguma.</seg>
			</tuv>
		</tu>
